netBotz_prd_bot_temp.name: netBotz_prd_bot_temp
netBotz_prd_bot_temp.description: The reading of the temperature probe, in degrees F or degrees C (depends on netBotz-ismetric).

netBotz_prd_bot_humidity.name: netBotz_prd_bot_humidity
netBotz_prd_bot_humidity.description: The reading of the humidity probe, in percent.

netBotz_prd_bot_airflow.name: netBotz_prd_bot_airflow
netBotz_prd_bot_airflow.description: The reading of the airflow probe. Each unit represents approximately 40 feet/minute or 13 meters/minute of airflow velocity.

netBotz_prd_bot_audio.name: netBotz_prd_bot_audio
netBotz_prd_bot_audio.description: The reading of the audio alarm probe on/off.

netBotz_prd_bot_doorajar.name: netBotz_prd_bot_doorajar
netBotz_prd_bot_doorajar.description: The reading of the door switch probe open(0) or closed(1).

netBotz_prd_bot_temp_min.name: netBotz_prd_bot_temp_min
netBotz_prd_bot_temp_min.description: The temperature probe minimum, from 35 to 120 degrees F, or 1 to 50 degrees C (depends on netBotz-ismetric).

netBotz_prd_bot_temp_max.name: netBotz_prd_bot_temp_max
netBotz_prd_bot_temp_max.description: The temperature probe maximum, from 35 to 120 degrees F, or 1 to 50 degrees C (depends on netBotz-ismetric).

netBotz_prd_bot_humidity_min.name: netBotz_prd_bot_humidity_min
netBotz_prd_bot_humidity_min.description: The humidity probe minimum, from 10 to 90 percent.

netBotz_prd_bot_humidity_max.name: netBotz_prd_bot_humidity_max
netBotz_prd_bot_humidity_max.description: The humidity probe maximum, from 10 to 90 percent.

netBotz_prd_bot_airflow_mins.name: netBotz_prd_bot_airflow_mins
netBotz_prd_bot_airflow_mins.description: Minutes without airflow before alarm set.

netBotz_prd_bot_audio_secs.name: netBotz_prd_bot_audio_secs
netBotz_prd_bot_audio_secs.description: Seconds of alarm audio before alarm set.

netBotz_prd_bot_temp_enabled.name: netBotz_prd_bot_temp_enabled
netBotz_prd_bot_temp_enabled.description: Temperature probe alarm enabled(1) or disabled(0).

netBotz_prd_bot_hum_enabled.name: netBotz_prd_bot_hum_enabled
netBotz_prd_bot_hum_enabled.description: Humidity probe alarm enabled(1) or disabled(0).

netBotz_prd_bot_air_enabled.name: netBotz_prd_bot_air_enabled
netBotz_prd_bot_air_enabled.description: Airflow probe alarm enabled(1) or disabled(0).

netBotz_prd_bot_audio_enabled.name: netBotz_prd_bot_audio_enabled
netBotz_prd_bot_audio_enabled.description: Audio probe alarm enabled(1) or disabled(0).

netBotz_prd_bot_switch_state.name: netBotz_prd_bot_switch_state
netBotz_prd_bot_switch_state.description: Switch state setting. The state controls which condition of the door switch indicates an alarm. If set to 0, alarm is set when the switch is closed. If set to 1, alarm is set when the switch is open.

netBotz_prd_bot_audio_level.name: netBotz_prd_bot_audio_level
netBotz_prd_bot_audio_level.description: Audio level setting. This is the relative audio level, from 0-11, above which an alarm will be sent.

netBotz_prd_bot_doorpic_delay.name: netBotz_prd_bot_doorpic_delay
netBotz_prd_bot_doorpic_delay.description: Number of seconds between door alert and first picture.

netBotz_prd_bot_trap_index.name: netBotz_prd_bot_trap_index
netBotz_prd_bot_trap_index.description: The crawler ID of the last trap.

netBotz_prd_bot_trap_address.name: netBotz_prd_bot_trap_address
netBotz_prd_bot_trap_address.description: The IP address of the last trap.

netBotz_prd_bot_trap_oid.name: netBotz_prd_bot_trap_oid
netBotz_prd_bot_trap_oid.description: The object id of the last trap.

netBotz_prd_bot_trap_value.name: netBotz_prd_bot_trap_value
netBotz_prd_bot_trap_value.description: The value of the last object trap.

netBotz_prd_bot_trap_date.name: netBotz_prd_bot_trap_date
netBotz_prd_bot_trap_date.description: The date and time of a specific trap. This field contains the number of seconds elapsed since midnight (00:00:00), January 1, 1970

netBotz_prd_bot_refresh.name: netBotz_prd_bot_refresh
netBotz_prd_bot_refresh.description: Rate of web page refresh, in seconds. This must be greater than 5 seconds.

netBotz_prd_bot_airflow_level.name: netBotz_prd_bot_airflow_level
netBotz_prd_bot_airflow_level.description: Airflow alert level. This is the relative level of airflow below which an alarm will be sent. The range is 1-11. Each unit is approximately 40 feet/second or 13 meters/second of airflow velocity.

netBotz_prd_bot_doorpic_count.name: netBotz_prd_bot_doorpic_count
netBotz_prd_bot_doorpic_count.description: Number of pictures to take when door activated. These pictures will be sent as attachments to the door alert e-mail. The range is from 0 to 5 pictures.
